Please follow the instructions in the request for evidence. If you do not receive your request for evidence by December 15, 2022, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
